content: I'm looking for some tips on organizing my garage. I've been putting it off for a while, but I think I'm finally ready to tackle it. Do you have any advice on how to get started and what to do with all the stuff I'll likely find in there? By the way, I had a bit of a scare recently when I misplaced a family heirloom, my grandmother's antique locket, and it really made me realize how important it is to keep my space organized.
